Detailed Description

CMML_Clip: an clip element as presented in the CMML document.
Examples:

cmml-seek-clip.c, cmml-seek-offset.c, cmml-seek-utc.c, cmml-uri-file.c, cmml-validate.c, and cmml-write.c.
